msgstr "Muntanyes i Mars"

#: addons/Mountains___Seas.wad/addon:5 input:6 input:10 standard
msgid "many mountains with high plateaus and many lakes. Version 1,0"
msgstr "moltes muntanyes amb altiplans i molts llacs. Versió 1,0"

#: addons/Mountains___Seas.wad/dirnames:4 standard input:4
msgid "Add-On Maps"
msgstr "Mapes del complement"

#: input:7 input:11 standard
msgid ""
"Game concept: You and your ally (blue) have an advantage—a connection via a "
"shared sea route. Play as a Headquarters Hunter and protect your partner if "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
"Concepte de joc: tu i el teu aliat (blau) tens un avantatge: una connexió "
"mitjançant una ruta marítima compartida. Juga com a caçador de la seu i "
"protegeix la teva parella si cal."
